sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 飞书用户
    participant H as CodexOpsHer
    participant S as codex-remote-control Skill
    participant B as Bridge Server
    participant W as Mac Worker
    participant A as codex app-server
    participant R as 本地 repo/shell

    U->>H: /codex carher-admin 查 deploy 风险
    H->>S: 命令硬路由 / Skill
    S->>B: POST /api/codex/tasks
    B->>B: 校验 her_uid/open_id/repo
    B->>W: WSS start_task
    W->>A: thread/start + turn/start
    A->>R: 读文件 / 搜索 / 申请命令审批
    A-->>W: streamed events
    W-->>B: output / approval / diff
    B-->>H: 飞书消息 / 卡片
    H-->>U: 输出和审批按钮
